Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course.roll

Class CourseRoll

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course.roll.CourseRoll
  • public class CourseRoll
extends java.lang.Object
    Course roll represents the roll of students as a linked abstract list for the course Students can enroll and drop in and out of the course roll.
    Author:
    Abby Bowyer, Neil Towne
